sentences.english: "The Nutcracker" is one of the most popular ballets in the world.

sentences.english: No power pack or spring clips needed, it works off a 9V battery.

sentences.chinese: 馬克每次用指頭彈了來自夾子的子彈一。

sentences.english: Go beyond the desk to drawers, shelves, coffee tables.

sentences.english: After she paid the bill, she placed the receipt in her wallet.
sentences.chinese: 她付了款之後把收據放進皮夾子裏。
